'''MSE-6-P303K''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[MSE-6 series repair droid/Legends|MSE-6 series repair droid]]. In [[8 ABY/Legends|8 ABY]] it was modified and controlled by the [[R2-series astromech droid/Legends|R2 unit]] [[Tonin]]. With scores of others, it was then used for the sabotage of [[Iron Fist (Executor-class)|''Iron Fist'']].

